# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [Unreleased]

## [1.0.0] - 2026-03-01

### Added

- Governance structure per [ADR-0014](docs/adr/ADR-0014.md) (WI-<DATE>-001)

## [0.9.0] - 2025-06-01

### Added

- Widget subsystem with drag-and-drop support
- Keyboard navigation for accessibility

### Fixed

- Race condition in event dispatcher (#42)

## [v0.8.0] - 2025-03-15

### Changed

- Migrated from Webpack to Vite
- Upgraded tokio to 1.28

### Deprecated

- Legacy plugin API (use v2 hooks instead)

## [0.7.0] - 2025-01-10

### Added

- Initial public release
- REST API with OpenAPI spec
